### Prerequisites

- [uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/) ≥ 0.5
- Python {{ python_version }} (managed by uv via `.python-version`)

### Common commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
{% if python == 'root' %}
| `uv run poe check` | Lint and type-check |
| `uv run poe test` | Run test suite |
| `uv run poe all` | Check + test |
| `uv run poe fmt` | Auto-format code |
{% elif python == 'component' %}
| `cd backend && uv run poe check` | Lint and type-check |
| `cd backend && uv run poe test` | Run test suite |
| `cd backend && uv run poe all` | Check + test |
| `cd backend && uv run poe fmt` | Auto-format code |
{% endif %}
{% endif %}
